Class ConnectionHandlerDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.guitools.controlpanel.datamodel.ConnectionHandlerDescriptor
  • public class ConnectionHandlerDescriptor
extends Object
    This class is used to represent a Listener and is aimed to be used by the classes in the ListenersTableModel class.
